description:
Rapper Problem and Rapper Meg Thee Stallion join the ladies of Lip Service this week to celebrate album releases and record deal signings. Things get nasty when Angela schools the guests on 'gaping,' Problem explains how he got all his baby mothers in one group chat, and much more! Enjoy!
